17:17.504 --> 17:19.572
Oh! Uh!

17:19.639 --> 17:21.408
Uh. Uh!

17:23.943 --> 17:26.746
The net! Velma, the net!

17:26.813 --> 17:28.481
Thud

17:34.821 --> 17:36.689
Freddy?

17:36.756 --> 17:38.391
Hang in there, fang boy!

17:38.458 --> 17:40.627
Thanks, Fred.
You saved my life.

17:40.693 --> 17:43.096
Actually, I was just
climbing down from the attic

17:43.163 --> 17:45.765
where I was trapped,
but you're welcome anyway.

17:45.832 --> 17:48.535
Uh, what happened?
Where's the vampire?

17:48.601 --> 17:49.436
Did he get away?

17:49.502 --> 17:51.604
Nope.
He's right over there.

17:51.671 --> 17:53.673
Oh, no, he's gone!

17:54.841 --> 17:56.075
Well, guess it looks like

17:56.143 --> 17:58.278
I won't be needing
these anymore.

17:59.979 --> 18:01.148
Thud

18:02.515 --> 18:06.853
Wow, I guess garlic really
does work on vampires.

18:06.919 --> 18:09.189
Yeah, that's the creep
who had me locked up too.

18:09.256 --> 18:10.557
'Be careful, Daphne.'

18:10.623 --> 18:13.560
Don't worry,
it's hypoallergenic.

18:13.626 --> 18:15.462
'Steve Fortescu?'

18:15.528 --> 18:18.531
Okay, so we've proven
Steve is the vampire.

18:18.598 --> 18:20.667
But we don't have a clue
who's been helping him

18:20.733 --> 18:22.068
escape from his cell.

18:22.135 --> 18:23.903
That's not exactly true.

18:23.970 --> 18:25.372
It's no makeup effect.

18:25.438 --> 18:27.874
'Steve and the vampire
look identical'

18:27.940 --> 18:29.542
'because they're twin brothers.'

18:29.609 --> 18:30.510
Of course!

18:30.577 --> 18:32.545
How else could anyone
be in two places

18:32.612 --> 18:36.416
