our video shoot.

18:50.763 --> 18:53.032
I think they wanted to scare
everybody off

18:53.099 --> 18:54.867
and ruin Owen's business.

18:54.934 --> 18:56.269
And it would have worked

18:56.336 --> 18:58.305
